{"type": "article", "id": 33365, "title": "拉好这根拉链，罐头很容易就打开了！｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-16T23:11:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 16082, "name": "SOHN"}, {"id": 33984, "name": "Another Studio"}, {"id": 33985, "name": "Haoshi Design"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 30564, "name": "OTOTO"}, {"id": 33986, "name": "Alon Dodo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 154, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161017071053KH935alA14FfJDgm.jpg", "contents": "<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Timber Tailor by Another Studio</h3><p>英国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.another-studio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Another Studio</a> 最近从服装剪裁中获得启发，用纸板裁剪技术对薄木片进行处理后制作出了四款让人联想到裙子的吊灯系列 Timber Tailor。不同的重叠方式打造出了多边形灯罩上不同的图案，加上顶部用做装饰的宽边折纸，看起来相当有趣。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.another-studio.com/shop?category=New%3A+Timber+Tailor#\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 195 英镑起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101617595384IduCrENvwRUxbH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.605134\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016175953LWtxSmIBcP5T70pX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016175953c8PUMan6VXskQJvG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016175953vxFheL9pA1YISy3t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016175953gxNid6Or90Hq5Jab.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016175954DJRcFYT6K1fi52m4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Migrantbird Clock by haoshi design</h3><p>台湾设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.haoshi.com.tw/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">haoshi</a> 以候鸟随着四季迁徙为主题，设计了一套漂亮的候鸟钟。时钟采用了本土制造的静音机芯，小巧的圆形钟面并没有刻度，上面搭配了两根纤细的指针，看上去相当简洁。haoshi 根据候鸟的飞行阵型设计了三种款式，通过附带的定位图可以很快地完成组装。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.haoshi.com.tw/en/series.php?se=CLOCK\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 160 和 170 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201610161802234hNiDsSuEQWe3mzG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.491803\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016180222dYcbClfi6QWm4OZq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.491803\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016180220QsxJHTGOX1Y8IByV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.491803\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201610161802209nC3fSLaDlst4HrF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.491803\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016180223hXYz4xdkwocTP3lj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.491803\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016180221awRDYPd92e4yAuim.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.491803\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Patch Match by Alon Dodo</h3><p>以色列设计师 <a href=\"http://www.alondodo.com/ChangeLanguage.asp?LangId=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alon Dodo</a> 以打造木制家具见长，硬邦邦的木料在他的作品中好像拥有了织布的特性，充满了有趣的细节。这张名为 <a href=\"http://www.alondodo.com/Default.asp?PageId=107936&amp;FragmentId=502454&amp;PagesCount=35&amp;sType=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Black Patch Match</a> 的桌子就是一个典型的例子，黑色的木板组成了大部分桌面，Dodo 别出心裁地将桌面的一角“缝”上了一块棕色的“补丁”，有了一种自带桌布的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016180202x5qXpdC9cTB0KefE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016180202794oDkVR5YuHWwbq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201610161802024VlgjEdBNqoJG6uQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016180202zH3wXfP8hk4NupIq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016180203Kkyj7cpawdF3z5nA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Oxygen Vase by ZAOZUO</h3><p>如果你喜欢开放式的花器，不妨看一看<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>的这款花瓶。水泥底座上是一个可以分离的立方体金属框，三面设置了八根平行的金属线。这种极简的结构在光照下形成的影子不断作着微妙的变化，像是捕捉到了时间一样，非常灵动。它既可用来摆放空气凤梨，又能当做桌面装饰搭配烛台等小物。这是它的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300145\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 122 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016193537Tnz0vw6c3BxhkFiY.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016193537fzWNDIlQ6TCE9eFB.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201610161935354d1Tf7K2JQFlnY35.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016193537Hw7Xm2hl48d1NeUn.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016193536PV6FSChRpHkjs53i.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Zip-Eat! by OTOTO</h3><p>还记得那个总是想用有意思的小物让你换一种方式解决一些生活小麻烦的以色列品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTOTO</a> 吗？这一截名为 Zip-Eat! 的大拉链就是专门为开罐所设计的，下次再碰到顽固的盖子，你就能借助拉链的力量把它拧开了。不用的时候把拉链收一收，还可以像其他厨房工具一样把它挂起来。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/all-products/products/zip-eat\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 16 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201610161946340MvzAm18VC3DBts6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.675676\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201610161946327jfKzOmLD3FYVMvH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201610161946329LyKHetwNUXhg6rE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016194634IXHl7cBqkTzewbCA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016194632rSpH3kKlXTELQZvn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Constellation candle holder by SOHN</h3><p>想在家里重现星座并不一定需要高端灯饰的帮助，韩国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.sohn.work/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SOHN</a> 最近就带来了一款以圆圈和直线构成的 <a href=\"http://www.sohn.work/constellation-candle-holder\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constellation</a> 烛台。它既可以容纳小小的茶蜡，也可以在支架里放入高一点的蜡烛，显得错落有致。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016204133SJjv9bDr72NKTlx8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.677500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016204133RNZAOKlEI7qD4sHY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016204134FKB7LMevJwisHtfR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.710000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016204133HN5D892pVCB0UEJP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016204134osDiErhOX90LNeuM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20161016204134USJwCt8zDpMmKd7a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div>"}